---------------------------------------------------GO TO ArrayInputString.java-------------------------------------

	We can create an array of size 0 in java

	during execution

	PARSE a string during the compilation in the command line

	java Program4 java sql j2ee  < --------- THis concept is called Command line arguments 

	the string passed above will be passed to the main function and will be stored in "String[] args" 

